title: #176: The Making of an Adult J Degenerate (@LuisJGomez)
itunes:title: The Making of an Adult J Degenerate with Luis J. Gomez
description: Luis J Gomez came over to my aparment to talk to me. I was trying to figure out how a guy like him was made. Where he came from. Luis is kind of a degenerate. He might disagree, but that's how I feel. So I wanted to see what makes someone become what I feel is a degen. It involves a mother who loves heroin and child abuse.
